            <title>[DERBY-2309] Add build.xml, so that the code can get compiled using ant with the &apos;all&apos; target.</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/DERBY-2309</link>
                <project id="10594" key="DERBY">Derby</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Place holder for adding build.xml. Also I propose here to create derbySysTest.jar instead of putting all the system test classes in the derbyTesting.jar. By doing that people who wish to run the system test only need to download them. All comments and suggestions are welcome&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
